			TrayLib
			Library for tray-like applets
			by Dennis Tomas

Brief 
~~~~~ 
TrayLib is a python module that eases the creation of tray-like applets. These
are applets that mainly consist of a box, which contains some icons 
representing some objects in the system.
It is used by TaskTray, DevTray and AppTray.

You need ROX-Lib2 to use it.

